 0.0, \"text\": \"National Democratic Alliance (NDA)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Democratic_Alliance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Democratic_Alliance\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"the 111th episode\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"his monthly radio program\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 143}, {\"ngram\": \"his gratitude\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 167}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said people reposed their unbreakable trust in the Constitution and the democratic process in elections.\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"their unbreakable trust\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"the Constitution\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"the democratic process\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"elections\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PM Modi also spoke about the upcoming Paris Olympics and urged the people to support and cheer the athletes and sportspersons participating in the mega event.\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modi\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"sportspersons\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the mega event\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also urged them to use '#cheer4Bh