\": \"11 foreign languages\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 110th episode of Mann Ki Baat, heemphasised the advancements made by women in society.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mann Ki Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 110th episode\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"the advancements\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PM Modi said that he had \\\"missed the communication\\\" since the last episode on February 25, when it was paused due to the electoral process.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modi\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the communication\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"the last episode\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"the electoral process\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today, finally the day has come for which we all have been waiting since February.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through 'Mann Ki Baat', I am once again amongst you, amongst my family members.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mann Ki Baat\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"my family members\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I told you in February that I would meet you again after the election results and today I am again present amongst you with Mann Ki Baat.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mann Ki Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the election results\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The arrival of Monsoon has made your hearts happy as well...\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monsoon\", \"score\": 0.9223030498537621, \"rank\": 0.08424232160835615, \"text\": \"Monsoon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monsoon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monsoon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The arrival\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"your hearts\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that though the radio broadcasts were paused for a while, its spirit continued in the country.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the radio broadcasts\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"its spirit\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Mann Ki Baat radio program might have been closed for a few months...but the spirit of Mann Ki Baat...work done for the country, the society good work done every day, work done with selfless spirit\\u2026work that had a positive impact on the society continued unabated,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mann Ki Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mann Ki Baat\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mann_Ki_Baat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few months\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"the society good work\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"selfless spirit\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive impact\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the society\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Modi thanked the voters for electing NDA for a third consecutive term.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Democratic_Alliance\", \"score\": 0.9972156888123888, \"rank\": 0.0027545225739925125, \"text\": \"NDA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Democratic_Alliance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Democratic_Alliance\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modi\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"the voters\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"a third consecutive term\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, \\\"Today I also thank the countrymen that they have reiterated their unwavering faith in our Constitution and the democratic system of the country.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the countrymen\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"their unwavering faith\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"our Constitution\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"the democratic system\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lok Sabha election 2024 was the biggest election in the world.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Lok Sabha election\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest election\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such a big election has never been held in any country of the world in which 65 crore people cast their votes.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such a big election\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"any country\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"65 crore people\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"their votes\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I congratulate the Election Commission and everyone associated with the electoral process.'\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.702850304839039e-13, \"text\": \"Election Commission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Election_Commission_of_India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"the electoral process\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"4.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The prime minister also wished the country on \\\"Hul Diwas\\\", celebrated across the country to commemorate the sacrifice of tribals for the nation.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prime minister\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"Hul Diwas\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifice\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"tribals\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today, June 30 is a very important day.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2794}, {\"ngram\": \"a very important day\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our tribal brothers and sisters celebrate this day as Hul Diwas.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2877, \"end\": 2880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hul\", \"score\": 0.9999999542392298, \"rank\": 4.5760571873105264e-08, \"text\": \"Hul\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our tribal brothers\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2842}, {\"ngram\": \"sisters\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This day is associated with the courage of Veer Sidhu and Kanhu who strongly opposed the atrocities of foreign rulers.\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2936, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navjot_Singh_Sidhu\", \"